<h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Reporting changes</h2>
<p>You must tell us straightaway if there is a change in your circumstances. If you give wrong or incomplete information, or you do not report changes, you may be paid more or less money than you should. You will have to pay back overpaid money when told to do so. You could also be prosecuted or need to pay a financial penalty. If we pay you less money than we should we may pay you this money back.</p>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-m">More information</h2>
